<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-310-598  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 310 598.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Macworld  May 1990 v7 n5 p373(2).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>The Art Importer 2.0; Fontographer 3.0. (Software Review)(PostScript font-design software) (evaluation)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Cummings, Steve.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>The Art Importer 2.0 is PostScript font-design software for theApple Macintosh Plus.andP;  The program makes it easy to createhigh-quality custom PostScript fonts and to import graphics filesfrom other sources.andP;  The major drawback is the limitation on fontsize and complexity due to printer memory.andP;  List price is $179.andO;Fontographer 3.0 is a companion package for the Mac Plus thatoffers a good selection of drawing tools and character-designaids.andP;  The program features a useful autotrace feature and offersPostScript and screen font hints.andP;  One minor drawback is the lackof one-step drawing tools for ovals, squares and rectangles.andP;  Listprice is $495.andP;  Both products come from Altsys Corp.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   Altsys Corp. (products).andO;Product:   Apple Macintosh Plus (Microcomputer) (computer programs)The Art Importer 2.0 (Computer graphics software)Fontographer (Computer program).andO;Topic:     FontsDesignSoftware PackagesEvaluation.andO;Feature:   illustrationphotograph.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>